            <b>Climate:</b> Warm & humid <br>
            <b>Soil:</b> Well-drained loamy <br>
            <b>Best Grown In:</b> Wayanad, Kozhikode, Palakkad <br>
            <b>Diseases:</b> Soft rot, Bacterial wilt <br>
            <b>Prevention:</b> Trichoderma treatment, raised beds, rotation.`;
          break;

        case "turmeric":
          recommendation = `<h4>üå± Turmeric</h4>
            <b>Season:</b> April‚ÄìJune <br>
