            <b>Climate:</b> Warm & humid <br>
            <b>Soil:</b> Fertile loamy <br>
            <b>Best Grown In:</b> Idukki, Wayanad, Palakkad <br>
            <b>Diseases:</b> Leaf spot, Rhizome rot <br>
            <b>Prevention:</b> Fungicide seed treatment, mulching, neem cake.`;
          break;

        case "cardamom":
          recommendation = `<h4>üåø Cardamom</h4>
            <b>Season:</b> June‚ÄìJuly <br>
            <b>Duration:</b> 2‚Äì3 years to yield <br>
            <b>Climate:</b> Cool, humid, shady <br>
            <b>Soil:</b> Rich forest loam <br>
            <b>Best Grown In:</b> Idukki, Wayanad <br>
            <b>Diseases:</b> Capsule rot, Leaf blotch <br>
            <b>Prevention:</b> Shade regulation, Trichoderma, drainage.`;
          break;

        case "rubber":
          recommendation = `<h4>üå≥ Rubber</h4>
            <b>Season:</b> June‚ÄìJuly <br>
            <b>Duration:</b> 6‚Äì7 years to yield <br>
            <b>Climate:</b> Warm, moist <br>
